I am pleased to inform you that we have successfully completed the migration of the **SM Project to JDK 21**. This milestone marks a significant step forward in ensuring our system’s compatibility with the latest technologies and performance improvements.  

With this achievement, we are now shifting our focus to the next phase of the project: **upgrading the Distributor and GUI components**. Our objectives for this phase include:  
- Enhancing the Distributor’s performance and scalability.  
- Modernizing the GUI to improve user experience and maintainability.  
- Ensuring seamless integration with the updated JDK 21 environment.  

